<p align="left">
In the offer list, all items are displayed with accompanying information.<br />
<br />
By default, NOT Cancelled entries are displayed. To view other entries, then<br />
please click on the arrow symbols (up = NOT Cancelled, Down = Cancelled, right = Show all).<br />
You can also change the sorted order. Standard Sort by Date (newest entries first).<br />
<br />
If you want to create a new offer, please click on New. You get<br />
now the offer mask. First, select a customer. After a<br />
customer has been chosen, additional customer information<br />
are indicated (account number, payment method, date, message etc.)<br />
Now you can add to the offer items, please click on Position / Article - [  New  ],<br />
then click Search. In the Position list please select the desired items.<br />
<br />
If you change data such as the date, then it is necessary either the TAB key to<br />
press or to click in another field for the changes to be adopted.<br />
After you click Save, the offer is stored. (Table: offer and offerpos).<br />
<br />
If you want to create an invoice from a offer, then please click in the offer list<br />
on the account icon (far right) or click the desired offer number.<br />
At the info-page please click on invoice. This will take you to the invoice mask.<br />
All data are from the offer automatically adopted in the invoice.<br />
<br />
Note:<br />
<br />
Offers can not be deleted. Offer can be cancelled from the info page.<br />
(Administrator and User Group Manager and Root)<br />
